OL,3,CCounter-terror police probe another
OL,4,Carson attack in north-west London
OL,6,FCounter-terror police are
OL,7,Finvestigating an arson attack in north-
OL,8,Fwest London "due to the similarities"
OL,9,Fwith recent incidents in the area.
OL,11,FPolice and the London Fire Brigade
OL,12,Fwere called at 10:31pm on Friday after
OL,13,Fa man set three bottles "containing
OL,14,Ffluid" alight outside a row of shops,
OL,15,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,17,FHe placed the bag by a building in
OL,18,FHendon before lighting the items
OL,19,Finside, it added.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@eO]uD@YOUvD@FO]
