CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776682974
OL,3,CCounter-terror police probe another
OL,4,Carson attack in north-west London
OL,6,FWhen they failed to fully ignite, the
OL,7,Fman fled the scene, the force said.
OL,9,FNo arrests have been made.
OL,11,FCounter Terrorism Policing London is
OL,12,Fleading the probe supported by the
OL,13,FMet's north-west command area.
OL,15,FIt is not being treated as a terrorist
OL,16,Fincident or is it currently being
OL,17,Flinked to other incidents in the area.
OL,19,FCommander Helen Flanagan, from Counter
OL,20,FTerrorism Policing London, said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776682974
OL,3,CCounter-terror police probe another
OL,4,Carson attack in north-west London
OL,6,F"At this stage last night's arson is
OL,7,Fnot being linked to other incidents in
OL,8,Fthe north-west London area over the
OL,9,Flast week or last month's arson in
OL,10,FGolders Green but Counter Terrorism
OL,11,Fofficers are leading due to the
OL,12,Fsimilarities of each attack.
OL,14,F"I would ask that anyone with
OL,15,Finformation or footage that could help
OL,16,Four investigation gets in touch with
OL,17,Fpolice as soon as possible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776682974
OL,3,CCounter-terror police probe another
OL,4,Carson attack in north-west London
OL,6,F"We will be relentless in our pursuit
OL,7,Fof those responsible for this and
OL,8,Fother, similar, hateful acts against
OL,9,FLondon's communities."
OL,11,FDetective Chief Superintendent Luke
OL,12,FWilliams, who leads policing in the
OL,13,Farea, said:
OL,15,F"Since the incident in Golders Green
OL,16,Flast month we have spoken extensively
OL,17,Fto community leaders.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776682974
OL,3,CCounter-terror police probe another
OL,4,Carson attack in north-west London
OL,6,F"I understand and appreciate their
OL,7,Fconcerns, and I know this latest
OL,8,Fincident will add to fears in the
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,F"Local officers are working closely
OL,12,Fwith counter-terrorism policing to
OL,13,Fsupport the investigation.
OL,15,F"The community can expect to see a
OL,16,Fheightened police presence in the
OL,17,Farea. Since last month's attack in
OL,18,FGolders Green, we have stepped up
OL,19,Fpolice patrols and vigilance to
OL,20,Freassure communities and disrupt
OL,21,Foffenders.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
