PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776682974
OL,3,CCounter-terror police probe another
OL,4,Carson attack in north-west London
OL,6,F"This includes armed police patrols as
OL,7,Fwell as deployments of officers from
OL,8,FProject Servator, who are specially
OL,9,Ftrained to spot anyone who may be
OL,10,Fplanning or preparing to commit
OL,11,Fcriminal acts."
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
